#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:129
#: bceba0d725f14a3d8ec5c66ad2adf51a
msgid ""
"目前支持完整的 GATT/SMP 等基础模块，支持自定义配置；已经实现的配置有 Bluetooth LE HID（设备端）、电池、DIS、Blu-"
"Fi（蓝牙配网）等。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:134
#: 6697a34fec084dbc8360545f2f26403a
msgid "如何使用 ESP32 蓝牙连接手机播放音乐？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:136
#: dc03aba33aff40929f2e7b2342944395
msgid ""
"用手机通过蓝牙播放音乐，ESP32 用作 A2DP Sink。A2DP Sink Demo 只是通过手机获取 SBC "
"编码的数据流，若要播放出声音，需要做编解码转换，通常需要编解码器、数/模转换器、扬声器等模块。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:141
#: 43539d4d95f84990b95861dbfa2dc5b6
msgid "ESP32 的 SPP 性能如何？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:143
#: b7b4dcaf709e4432906534a964eb7c79
msgid "使用两块 ESP32 开发板对跑 SPP，单向吞吐量量可达 1900 Kbps，约 235 KB/s，已接近规范里的理论值。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:148
#: 78208a796c3c463fb6d31c480f2d8ca3
msgid "ESP32 的 Bluetooth® LE 传输速率最大为多少？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:150
#: 536bca4075c84e12b330c13d1b69332a
msgid "屏蔽箱测试 Bluetooth LE 传输速率可以达到 800 Kbps。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:155
#: c45e185147844d00b45520117120298b
msgid "ESP32 Bluetooth® LE 如何进入 Light-sleep 模式呢？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:157
#: 37ae3fc9f0d748aa829dba8a571e7de3
msgid "硬件上需要外加 32 kHz 的外部晶振，否则 Light-sleep 模式不会生效。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:159
#: 0883e21345b947d8a8fda6044f0a7deb
msgid "软件上（SDK4.0 以及以上版本才会支持）在 menuconfig 中需要使能以下配置："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:161
#: 1ce4e628a0184bc2b67ac3b6f84c1f08
msgid ""
"Power Management:| menuconfig ---> Component config ---> Power management"
" --->[*] Support for power management"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:163
#: 365a3638f02c4d71aae6ae9ab710a5f5
msgid ""
"Tickless Idle:| menuconfig ---> Component config ---> FreeRTOS --->[*] "
"Tickless idle support (3) Minimum number of ticks to enter sleep mode for"
" (NEW)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:165
#: b834aa0853764a589ecd8774abf42ec6
msgid ""
"需使能 \"Tickless idle\" 功能使 ESP32 自动进入 Light-sleep 模式。如果在 3 个节拍（默认）内无任务运行，则"
" FreeRTOS 将进入 Light-sleep 模式，即 100 Hz 节拍率下为 30 ms。若您希望缩短 Light-sleep "
"模式的持续时间，可通过将 FreeRTOS 节拍率调高来实现，如：menuconfig ---> Component config ---> "
"FreeRTOS ->(1000) Tick rate (Hz)。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst
#: 97f02c2e3dbc4e568ea3946c2838fa94
msgid ""
"Configure external 32.768Hz crystal as RTC clock source :| menuconfig "
"---> Component config ---> ESP32-specific --->RTC clock source (External "
"32kHz crystal)[*] Additional current for external 32kHz crystal"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:169
#: a84ea6cd391846b297c395e983a04cb5
msgid ""
"\"additional current\" 选项为解决 ESP32 晶振失败的替代方案。请在您使用外部 32 kHz "
"晶体时使能该选项。该硬件问题将在下一个 ECO 芯片中解决。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst
#: 68598a15de104b008566db3ccfff977d
msgid ""
"Enable Bluetooth modem sleep with external 32.768kHz crystal as low power"
" clock :| menuconfig ---> Component config ---> Bluetooth ---> Bluetooth "
"controller ---> MODEM SLEEP Options --->[*] Bluetooth modem sleep"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:176
#: 9987abbd7702454bbcf160a8f58ed3aa
msgid "选择 ESP32 芯片实现蓝牙配网的方式，是否有文档可以提供参考？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:178
#: 8db22df018df4c3c82303395eab933be
msgid ""
"蓝牙配网说明可参考 `ESP32 Blufi <https://docs.espressif.com/projects/esp-"
"idf/zh_CN/latest/esp32/api-"
"guides/blufi.html?highlight=blufi>`_。蓝牙配网示例可以参考 `Blufi "
"<https://github.com/espressif/esp-"
"idf/tree/master/examples/bluetooth/bluedroid/ble/blufi>`_。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:183
#: e3b0ea0b75264ff7b504e23afc38af25
msgid "ESP32 经典蓝牙 SPP 的传输速率能达到多少？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:185
#: d46e95abca8d45fcb5faef1746d10fc8
msgid "在开放环境下，双向同时收发，实测可达到 1400+ Kbps 到 1590 Kbps（此数据仅作为参考，实际情况建议客户根据应用环境实测）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:190
#: 09c96432f3c943dcb9f30b353fb822bb
msgid "ESP32 的蓝牙是否兼容 Bluetooth® ver2.1 + EDR 协议？"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:192
#: 9d36a69aeb284297b1b258d26f38c686
msgid ""
"兼容。ESP32 的蓝牙是向下兼容的，您可以使用官方的 `蓝牙示例 <https://github.com/espressif/esp-"
"idf/tree/master/examples/bluetooth>`_ 进行测试。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/espressif/ble-bt.rst:197
